{"id": "1408689223044829237", "channel_id": "1408429441088225393", "type": 0, "author_id": "249051967219826690", "author_name": "nero_aliapoh", "author_bot": false, "content": "technically there's actual Arithmetica Limit, but the problem is, the term \"Arithmetica Limit\" in the game is used as the same meaning of \"Max Arithmetica\" for now, like in relics", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T05:48:02.954000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408429441088225393", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Max Arithmetica(最大算力) / Arithmetica Limit(算力上限)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1410391772894330961", "1412867280844357813"]}
{"id": "1408689870049902772", "channel_id": "1408429441088225393", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "but yeah there really shouldn't be any use in referring to your Arithmetica Limit in this game.\nHere, final answer on terminology:\n## - Max Arithmetica\n  - The amount of Arithmetica that you begin your turn with, shown on the bottom-left of the screen by (N)/**(X)**. Default is 5.\n## - Arithmetica Limit\n  - The highest amount of Arithmetica you're allowed to hold at once, beyond which any further Arithmetica gained is reduced to 0. *(or, in Astral Reign, converted into Keyflare.)*\n\n## In all cases currently in the game, any instance of these two terms should be errata'd to Max Arithmetica.\nIf at some point in the future it's discovered an error was made by this decision, it will be correct at that point and you can blame me.", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T05:50:37.212000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-24T18:14:20.810000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408429441088225393", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Max Arithmetica(最大算力) / Arithmetica Limit(算力上限)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1410391772894330961", "1412867280844357813"]}
