{"id": "1408695927924850759", "channel_id": "1408429441088225393", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "eh, I can't find a much better term right off the bat, so I think it'll do fine for now. I agree that it's not perfect though, but here's a fundamental rule of game design I learned by studying Magic:\n\nIn the same way that one of the basic principles that makes Comedy funny is a break from expectations, one of the basic principles that makes games fun is breaking \"the rules\".\nIt's always important to present players learning a game with what appears to be \"This is what you're allowed to do in this game\" so that they can understand the framework of what is and isn't \"supposed to be allowed\", so that when you *allow them to do something they didn't think you would let them do,* they have a good time.\n\n\"Max Arithmetica\" does in fact communicate the fact that, in the context of this genre of game, you're supposed to refresh your resources to their maximum at the start of each turn, and whatever your \"Max Arithmetica\" is, is what you expect that resource to recover to. Then later on, when you're presented a mechanic that tells you \"Hey! Did you know if you do *this*, you can go *above* your Max Arithmetica? and if you do *this other thing*, you can increase your Max Arithmetica!\", you understand from what basis you can evaluate that effect, and feel good that you're getting more powerful.", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T06:14:41.522000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "celestepray", "emoji_id": "1397414070100951110", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "casiah_cute", "emoji_id": "1408324282895040572", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408429441088225393", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Max Arithmetica(最大算力) / Arithmetica Limit(算力上限)", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1410391772894330961", "1412867280844357813"]}
