{"id": "1408656601837207562", "channel_id": "1407785080025383157", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "After working on the story I have concluded that these were indeed the effects of an overzealous find+replace - there's an instance of a line which clearly meant extradimensional just using the word \"ultra\" randomly, and \"Chaos\" as a term is randomly capitalized in various lines where it makes no sense to differentiate it and the chinese term being used is the same as the realm", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T03:38:25.452000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407785080025383157", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Use of realms as terminology", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867280844357813"]}
{"id": "1408656687208071219", "channel_id": "1407785080025383157", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "As such I plan to just use the correct words in context rather than the realm names since that was clearly not the original intention", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T03:38:45.806000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407785080025383157", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Use of realms as terminology", "forum_channel_id": "1404748432328888401", "thread_tags": ["1404748529724952576", "1412867280844357813"]}
